OL,3,CVoters to go to the polls in Gorton
OL,4,Cand Denton by-election
OL,6,FPolling stations have opened in a by-
OL,7,Felection that will see Gorton and
OL,8,FDenton's next MP elected.
OL,10,FEleven candidates are standing for the
OL,11,Fseat which became vacant after the
OL,12,Fresignation of Andrew Gwynne, who
OL,13,Fstood down because of ill health.
OL,15,FPeople are reminded to take a valid
OL,16,Fphoto ID with them, and have until
OL,17,F10pm to cast their vote.
